---
import '../../../styles/global.css';
---

<!-- SVG Header -->
<div class="w-screen flex justify-center lg:justify-start lg:-ml-[18.5rem] overflow-hidden relative pb-10" style="margin-left: calc(-50vw + 50%); margin-right: calc(-50vw + 50%);">
  <img 
    src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}/assets/images/ALife Slide Template-03 1.svg`} 
    alt="ALife Mission Header" 
    class="w-screen min-w-screen"
  />
  <!-- Centered Logo -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center">
    <img 
      src={`${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}/assets/logo/logo.svg`} 
      alt="ALIFE Logo" 
      class="h-8 sm:h-12 md:h-16 lg:h-18 w-auto opacity-90"
    />
  </div>
</div>

<!-- Mission Content -->
<div class="w-full px-4 sm:px-6 md:px-8 lg:px-12 pt-6 sm:pt-8 md:pt-10 pb-8 sm:pb-12 md:pb-16 relative">
  <!-- Flex Container for Mission, Vision, and Values -->
  <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-8 sm:gap-10 lg:gap-12 relative z-10 justify-between max-w-6xl mx-auto">
    
    <!-- Mission Section -->
    <div class="flex-1">
      <h2 class="text-4xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-5xl text-primary mb-2 sm:mb-3 md:mb-4" style="font-family: 'GT Alpina Fine', serif;">Mission</h2>
      <div class="h-0.5 w-16 sm:w-20 md:w-24 bg-primary mb-3 sm:mb-4 md:mb-6"></div>
      <p class="text-base sm:text-lg md:text-xl lg:text-20px text-primary leading-relaxed text-left" style="font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; line-height: 1.5; font-weight: 300; text-align: left;">
        To cultivate symbiotic relationships between humans and artificial life through open-ended evolutionary systems that continuously generate novel solutions to complex real-world challenges.
      </p>  
    </div>

    <!-- Vision Section -->
    <div class="flex-1">
      <h2 class="text-4xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-5xl text-primary mb-2 sm:mb-3 md:mb-4" style="font-family: 'GT Alpina Fine', serif;">Vision</h2>
      <div class="h-0.5 w-16 sm:w-20 md:w-24 bg-primary mb-3 sm:mb-4 md:mb-6"></div>
      <p class="text-base sm:text-lg md:text-xl lg:text-20px text-primary leading-relaxed text-left" style="font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; line-height: 1.5; font-weight: 300; text-align: left;">
        A future where artificial life forms work alongside humans as creative collaborators. We're curious about what happens when natural and artificial approaches to problem-solving combine, creating new possibilities that neither humans nor machines would discover working separately.
      </p>
    </div>

     <!-- Values Section -->
    <div class="flex-1">
      <h2 class="text-4xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-5xl text-primary mb-2 sm:mb-3 md:mb-4" style="font-family: 'GT Alpina Fine', serif;">Values</h2>
      <div class="h-0.5 w-16 sm:w-20 md:w-24 bg-primary mb-3 sm:mb-4 md:mb-6"></div>
      <div class="space-y-3">
        <div>
          <strong class="text-base sm:text-lg md:text-xl lg:text-20px text-primary font-medium">Open-Endedness:</strong>
          <span class="text-base sm:text-lg md:text-xl lg:text-20px text-primary font-light"> We believe in systems that explore without predetermined goals, discovering paths no one planned</span>
        </div>
        <div>
          <strong class="text-base sm:text-lg md:text-xl lg:text-20px text-primary font-medium">Symbiosis:</strong>
          <span class="text-base sm:text-lg md:text-xl lg:text-20px text-primary font-light"> Rather than replacement, we seek harmonious coexistence between human and artificial intelligence</span>
        </div>
        <div>
          <strong class="text-base sm:text-lg md:text-xl lg:text-20px text-primary font-medium">Emergence:</strong>
          <span class="text-base sm:text-lg md:text-xl lg:text-20px text-primary font-light"> We embrace complexity and unexpected outcomes as sources of breakthrough innovation</span>
        </div>
        <div>
          <strong class="text-base sm:text-lg md:text-xl lg:text-20px text-primary font-medium">Curiosity:</strong>
          <span class="text-base sm:text-lg md:text-xl lg:text-20px text-primary font-light"> We prioritize exploration and surprise over efficiency and predictability</span>
        </div>
        <div>
          <strong class="text-base sm:text-lg md:text-xl lg:text-20px text-primary font-medium">Collaboration:</strong>
          <span class="text-base sm:text-lg md:text-xl lg:text-20px text-primary font-light"> Our best discoveries come from diverse minds working together across disciplines</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

